sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor OP as Operator or Scheduler
    participant JOB as train_staging_models_and_forecasts.py
    participant CDB as Cleansing DB
    participant MAN as vault_manifest.db
    participant PART as VAULT partition DBs
    participant RES as In-Memory Resampler
    participant TRN as Model Trainer
    participant CORE as Forecast DB (core_kpi)
    participant FS as Model Filesystem

    OP->>JOB: Start training run
    JOB->>CDB: Query cleansing_run_id and training cutoff
    CDB-->>JOB: cleansing scope and cutoff timestamp
    JOB->>MAN: Discover pair scope and matching partitions before cutoff
    MAN-->>JOB: pruned partition list per pair

    loop each exchange and symbol pair
        JOB->>PART: Load raw history rows ts < cutoff
        PART-->>JOB: raw history rows
        JOB->>RES: Resample to bin_seconds
        RES-->>JOB: training frame
        JOB->>TRN: Train Ridge and HistGBR for both horizons
        TRN-->>JOB: fitted models and metrics
        JOB->>FS: Persist model artifacts
        FS-->>JOB: artifact paths
        JOB->>CDB: Load cleansing rows for inference horizon alignment
        CDB-->>JOB: inference rows
        JOB->>CORE: Upsert model registry rows and predictions
    end

    JOB-->>OP: Training summary and run status
